INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('270', '1', '2013-10-23 07:01:14', '2013-10-23 07:01:14', '<h1>New York Civil Trial Litigation Attorney</h1>\r\n<em>I am a trial lawyer based in Long Island, New York with a highly personalized practice in both State and Federal Courts here in New York and other states.</em>\r\n\r\nMy practice consists of diverse civil litigation with a concentration in representing plaintiffs who have been monetarily, physically or reputationally injured. This office handles a wide variety of civil litigation ranging from business disputes and securities fraud to libel, sexual harassment and medical malpractice.\r\n\r\nThis office combines the personalized attention to your case that is only available in a boutique law firm, with the resources of large firms. By partnering with large firms for larger cases, and establishing working relationships favorable to my clients, I have delivered small firm personalized attention with large firm manpower and support resources.\r\n\r\nThe challenge of winning motions and trials often depends upon the lawyer\'s ability to simplify the complex and strike a resonant theme. At its core litigating a case consists of communicating a story. To the victim of wrongful treatment it is perhaps the most important story they have to tell. I consider it a gift to have a vocation which enables me to provide such a service.\r\n\r\nEdward Miller is a civil trial attorney with thirty years of experience in cases ranging from libel and slander to securities class actions. In the late 90\'s, Mr.Miller led a trial team of four different law firms in the consolidated cases Webb vs. United Automobile Workers in central Illinois, and in 2005 through 2008 Miller led a trial team in a series of lawsuits against the New York State Department of Corrections.\r\n\r\nHaving appeared on ABC World News Tonight and Court T.V.in connection with high profile cases, Miller has won all but two of the over twenty jury trials he has taken to verdict.\r\n\r\nAt the conclusion of his first jury trial, Cuyahoga County Court of Common Pleas Judge R. Donahue wrote of Miller:\r\n\r\n“Particularly in light of the clear and unarguable nature of the uniqueness of this case Mr. Miller has demonstrated skill, attention and ability in achieving the final jury result.”', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-23 07:01:14', '2013-10-23 07:01:14', '', '29', 'http://brentbowen.com/29-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('271', '1', '2013-10-23 07:08:40', '2013-10-23 07:08:40', '<h1>High Caliber Denton Legal Representation: <br />\r\nThe Bowen Law Group</h1>\r\nHandling complex legal issues can be extremely overwhelming, confusing, and stressful. It is vital to have an experienced advocate that can give advice and fight on your behalf, to keep your rights protected. When you need an attorney in Denton, Texas that you can trust, The Bowen Law Group certainly has the level of expertise that you will need. Each Denton attorney in our office concentrates in particular types of cases in many specific areas of law. Whether you need a Denton DWI attorney, a reputable Denton County divorce lawyer, a Denton criminal attorney, or a Frisco family lawyer for any other type of legal need in all areas of criminal and family law, you can count on professionalism, integrity, diligence, and experience with The Bowen Law Group. There is no need to take a chance by representing yourself pro se, when our lawyers are knowledgeable, skilled, and are more than willing to help you with everything from complex criminal defenses to family law issues.\r\n\r\n</h2>Why Choose The Bowen Law Group?</h2>\r\n\r\nWe practice in Denton, Collin, Wise and Cooke Counties.  Whether you need a Lewisville divorce lawyer, or a seasoned Denton family law attorney to help with your case, we can put our expertise to work on your behalf. Our office proudly serves clients in Denton County, Flower Mound, Lewisville, Frisco, and the surrounding areas. Our attorneys understand that time is of the essence where your issues are concerned, and we will do everything within our power to get the results that you want professionally, effectively, and efficiently. Our attorneys are personable, and they are totally committed to the needs of our valued clients. Our Denton divorce attorney professionals and our Denton criminal lawyers are highly respected in the local communities that we serve, for our diligence and the comprehensive approaches that we take, to ensure that our clients get the best legal representation possible.\r\n\r\n<h2>Case Types That We Handle</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>DWI Cases and Drug Crimes</li>\r\n    <li>Assault, Burglary, Theft, and Robbery Cases</li>\r\n    <li>Non-Disclosure and Expunction</li>\r\n    <li>Probation Violations</li>\r\n    <li>Juvenile Law</li>\r\n    <li>Divorce, Child Custody, Child Support, Enforcement, and Modifications</li>\r\n    <li>All Other Types of Family Law and Criminal Law Cases</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact Us Today!</h2>\r\n\r\nFor a criminal or divorce lawyer in Denton or the surrounding areas that you can count on, contact us today at [number type=\"1\"]. We will be more than happy to answer your inquiries, or to schedule an appointment so that you can consult with our lawyers about your case.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-23 07:08:40', '2013-10-23 07:08:40', '', '29', 'http://brentbowen.com/29-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
