INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('290', '1', '2013-10-23 10:03:20', '2013-10-23 10:03:20', '<iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/esn8sg7TDWk?rel=0&amp;wmode=opaque\" height=\"338\" width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n\r\nA criminal conviction, even a misdemeanor conviction, can have severe repercussions. If you have been charged with a crime, it is critical to obtain legal counsel to protect your rights.\r\n\r\nAt Bowen Law Group, we provide experienced and aggressive defense services on behalf of adults and juveniles charged with a crime. With offices in Denton and Lewisville, Texas, we are pleased to represent clients throughout the region, including people in Denton, Dallas, Tarrant, Wise, and Cooke counties.\r\n\r\nWe handle a wide range of felony and misdemeanor criminal law matters, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>DUI / DWI</li>\r\n	<li>Assault, including sexual assault</li>\r\n	<li>Injury to child/elderly</li>\r\n	<li>Drug possession and other drug crimes</li>\r\n	<li>Burglary and robbery</li>\r\n	<li>Probation violation</li>\r\n	<li>Expunction and nondisclosures</li>\r\n	<li>Juvenile law</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative license review hearing</li>\r\n	<li>Occupational driver’s license protection</li>\r\n	<li>Hearings, trial, sentencing, appeal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Former Prosecutors Protecting Your Rights</h3>\r\nThe attorneys at our firm are former prosecutors. In fact, Attorney Brent D. Bowen was a prosecutor for Shawnee County, Johnson County and Denton County. This experience better enables us to see both sides of a case and thoroughly scrutinize evidence on behalf of the clients we represent.\r\n<h3>Legal Assistance Tailored to Your Needs</h3>\r\nWhen handling a criminal law case, our goal is to provide immediate and long-term assistance to the people we represent. In some cases, litigation works best to serve the needs of clients. In other cases, a plea agreement resulting in a reduced charge or reduction of criminal penalties may be best. We will pursue whichever option leads to the better result.\r\n\r\nIn each case we handle, we place a strong emphasis on providing lasting results for the client we represent. Many people who are arrested on criminal charges are facing difficult personal challenges that may involve chemical dependency, mental illness or anger management issues. In cases where clients may benefit from assistance and ask for our help, we are pleased to provide assistance with the location of appropriate medical and mental health professionals.\r\n<h3>Contact a Texas Criminal Defense Attorney</h3>\r\nTo schedule a free consultation to learn more about your rights and options, call our Denton office at [number type=\"1\"] or contact our criminal defense lawyers by e-mail.', 'Criminal Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'criminal-defense', '', '', '2013-10-30 09:27:31', '2013-10-30 09:27:31', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.com/?page_id=290', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('291', '1', '2013-10-23 10:04:25', '2013-10-23 10:04:25', '<iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/yv8Wmw0alIQ?rel=0\" height=\"338\" width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n\r\nThe lawyers at Bowen Law Group are committed to helping families seek efficient and productive solutions to difficult family disputes. If you need to speak with a lawyer about a divorce or family law matter in the counties of Denton, Dallas, Tarrant, Wise or Cooke, we are pleased to be of assistance.\r\n\r\nWe take an aggressive yet reasoned approach to divorce and family disputes that has enabled many of our clients to achieve legal and personal closure in a relatively short period of time. We always put the interests of our clients first, and we will not fight or cause undue delay for the sake of pride or profit.\r\n\r\nContact us for assistance with any of the following family law matters:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Divorce</li>\r\n	<li>Property division</li>\r\n	<li>Child custody and visitation</li>\r\n	<li>Adoption</li>\r\n	<li>Defense of parents in Child Protective Services (CPS) investigations</li>\r\n	<li>Family law Mediation</li>\r\n	<li>Suit affecting parent-child relationship (SAPCR)</li>\r\n	<li>Protective and Restraining Orders</li>\r\n	<li>Modifications</li>\r\n	<li>Domestic Violence</li>\r\n	<li>Ad litem services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Protecting Your Rights in Family Law Cases</h3>\r\nOur goal in each case is to help people protect their financial and parental rights. Our attorneys are skilled negotiators and family court trial lawyers who have achieved positive results for clients in family law disputes involving complex division of property issues. When forming divorce settlements, we vigorously fight for the rights of the parents while keeping the best interests of the children in mind.\r\n<h3>Schedule an Appointment With a Texas Attorney</h3>\r\nIt is important to speak with a lawyer and fully understand your rights and responsibilities if you are involved in a legal dispute involving a spouse or children. We offer a very informative consultation. We give clients a candid assessment of their case so they may proceed in an informed manner.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about your rights and options, call our Denton office at [number type=\"1\"]. You may also contact us by e-mail.', 'Family Law', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'family-law', '', '', '2013-10-30 09:42:03', '2013-10-30 09:42:03', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.com/?page_id=291', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('292', '1', '2013-10-23 10:05:06', '2013-10-23 10:05:06', '<h2>Texas Law Firm Creating Smart Planning Solutions</h2>\r\nAccording to some experts, two-thirds of Americans do not have an estate plan in place. Unfortunately, this may leave them or the people they care about in a difficult situation. At Bowen Law Group, we believe in smart planning for the future. Lawyers at our Denton, Texas, law firm help clients draft estate plans that protect the people they care about.\r\n\r\nCreate an estate plan that protects the people you care about. Call [number type=\"1\"] to get started.\r\n<h3>Estate Planning</h3>\r\n<h4>Denton Estate Planning Attorneys</h4>\r\nBowen Law Group, located in Denton County, provides advice and a variety of estate planning services for individuals. When assisting a client in drafting a will or trust, our estate planning Attorneys are sensitive to the impact our services will have on our client’s emotional and economic well-being. When helping a client with estate planning, Bowen Law Group, located in Denton County, works to achieve a solution that will effectively protect the client’s interests and ensure his or her intentions will be carried out. Estate Planning is a process that requires careful listening and thorough preparation and attention to detail, at Bowen Law Group our attorneys are committed to providing that quality of legal counsel.\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you need a lawyer to write a will?</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you do not have a large estate, you may be considering drafting your own will, health care directive/living will/physician directive, and durable power of attorney, the documents that every adult should have in place. We urge you to reconsider. By preparing your own documents you run the chance of a document missing essential elements, leaving the estate at risk. If you would like to discuss your estate planning needs, please contact Bowen Law Groups Denton County Office. There is no charge for your initial consultation.\r\n<h4>Our estate planning services</h4>\r\nOur attorneys are prepared to assist clients with a full range of estate planning services:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Preparation of wills</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of living wills/health care directives</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of Powers of Attorney</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting trusts, including testamentary trusts, trusts for minors, disability trusts, and living trusts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAn experienced wills and trusts lawyer should be able to advise you in all of your estate planning needs with the foresight and precision writing a will demands. From simple wills, living wills, testamentary trust wills and other estate planning tools, a Bowen Law Group wills and trusts attorney can help you make the decisions that will benefit your loved ones the most.**\r\n\r\n<em>**We are Not Certified Professional Accountants, we advise you to allow us to consult with a CPA to protect your interests.</em>\r\n\r\nWhen properly written, an estate plan gives your loved ones the legal protections they deserve and the guidance they need to make difficult decisions.\r\n\r\nAn estate plan is more than just a will. A complete estate plan may include several documents, depending on your needs:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wills</li>\r\n	<li>Trusts</li>\r\n	<li>Powers of attorney</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced healthcare directives</li>\r\n	<li>Guardianships or conservatorships</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Probate</h3>\r\nOur law firm also guides clients through the Texas probate process. Probate and estate administration can often be time consuming and complex, but it is easier with the help of a knowledgeable lawyer who can answer your questions about how the law may apply in your case.\r\n<h3>Contact Bowen Law Group</h3>\r\nTo talk about estate planning or probate with an attorney at Bowen Law Group, please contact our Denton, Texas, law office at [number type=\"1\"]. Our phones are answered 24 hours a day, seven days a week so you can get quick responses to your legal concerns — especially when you need them most.', 'Estate Planning and Probate', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'estate-planning-and-probate', '', '', '2013-10-30 09:39:26', '2013-10-30 09:39:26', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.com/?page_id=292', '0', 'page', '', '0');
