rial. In either situation, it is critical for you to partner with a qualified divorce lawyer who can look out for your best interests.\r\n<h3>Meet Chrysandra S. Bowen</h3>\r\nChrysandra S. Bowen is an organized, efficient divorce lawyer who manages all divorce cases at our law firm in Denton, Texas. Her background in therapy and counseling enables her to help resolve family conflicts and generate creative solutions that fit her clients’ needs. She recognizes that you are more than the details of your case, and will treat you with consideration and respect every step of the way.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nIf you live in Denton area and are facing a divorce, contact  our law office at [number type=\"1\"]. Our phones are answered 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, so you can receive quick responses to your most pressing legal concerns. Our attorneys handle dissolution of marriage cases for clients throughout North Texas, including Lewisville, Denton, Flower Mound and other surrounding areas.  Contact us today!', 'Divorce', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '348-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-23 10:57:22', '2013-10-23 10:57:22', '', '348', 'http://brentbowen.com/348-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
