INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('411', '1', '2013-10-26 07:55:39', '2013-10-26 07:55:39', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Criminal Defense for Assault Allegations</h2>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/phikvDuso2A?rel=0\" height=\"338\" width=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n\r\nWhen allegations of violence lead to an arrest, the situation is often difficult and emotional. At Bowen Law Group, in Denton, Texas, we offer confidential and non-judgmental criminal defense that helps you achieve positive results in Texas state courts.\r\n\r\nAt Bowen Law Group, criminal defense lawyer Brent Bowen is a former Denton County assistant district attorney who is respected by prosecutors. Brent has a reputation for straight talk and effective action in Texas state courts.\r\n<h3>Representing People Accused of Violent Crimes in Texas State Courts</h3>\r\nWe represent people accused of a wide range of violent crimes, including assault, sexual assault and other violent conduct. We also handle family law disputes, like assault allegations related to domestic violence or allegations of child abuse made by Child Protective Services (CPS). Attorney Chrysandra Bowen handles these family issues with the attention and sensitivity they deserve, using her counseling background.\r\n\r\nWhen we take your assault case, we begin exploring all your options. Sometimes self defense is an effective explanation for your actions. Other times, witnesses are not credible. Regardless of the situation, our aim is to achieve positive results. However, there are times when the clients would benefit from anger management or family counseling.\r\n\r\nTexas law has changed. Now homeowners have no duty to retreat before defending themselves against dangerous intruders in their own homes. However, because each situation is unique, it is best to talk about your situation with an experienced lawyer.\r\n<h3>Contact Bowen Law Group</h3>\r\nTo talk about the assault allegations you face with an attorney at Bowen Law Group, please contact our Denton, Texas, law office at [number type=\"1\"]. Our phones are answered 24 hours a day, seven days a week so you can get quick responses to your legal concerns — especially when you need them most.', 'Assault', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '331-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-26 07:55:39', '2013-10-26 07:55:39', '', '331', 'http://www.brentbowen.com/331-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('412', '1', '2013-10-26 07:57:44', '2013-10-26 07:57:44', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Understanding and Effective Texas Divorce Lawyer</h2>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/XJb5rkxr5b4?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>The end of a marriage can be a very difficult thing to face. Even under the most amicable circumstances, divorce is a stressful and draining process for everyone involved, and the longer divorce proceedings last, the higher the emotional, mental and financial cost for a family.</p>\r\n<p>That’s why the attorneys at Bowen Law Group in Denton, Texas, work hard to resolve divorce cases as quickly and amicably as possible. The right lawyer can make a huge difference in how your divorce plays out, and our goal is to help you achieve maximum results with minimal stress for you and your loved ones.</p>\r\n<h3>What Happens during a Texas Divorce</h3>\r\n<p>Each divorce is unique. However, divorce proceedings in Texas usually start when one spouse files a petition for divorce, which requests that the court terminate the marriage based on either fault-based or no-fault-based grounds. The other spouse must then file an answer to the petition within a set period of time.</p>\r\n<p>Dissolution of marriage in Texas can involve a number of issues, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Child custody and visitation</li>\r\n<li>Determination of child support</li>\r\n<li>Determination of alimony (spousal support)</li>\r\n<li>Division of property and debt</li>\r\n<li>Domestic violence and restraining orders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In many cases, divorce attorneys in Texas help the two parties attempt to reach a settlement, often using dispute resolution methods such as mediation or arbitration. If they are successful, the agreement is submitted to a judge, who approves it and grants the divorce. However, in the event a settlement cannot be reached, or the judge does not give approval, your divorce may proceed to trial. In either situation, it is critical for you to partner with a qualified divorce lawyer who can look out for your best interests.</p>\r\n<h3>Meet Chrysandra S. Bowen</h3>\r\n<p>Chrysandra S. Bowen is an organized, efficient divorce lawyer who manages all divorce cases at our law firm in Denton, Texas. Her background in therapy and counseling enables her to help resolve family conflicts and generate creative solutions that fit her clients’ needs. She recognizes that you are more than the details of your case, and will treat you with consideration and respect every step of the way.</p>\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\n<p>If you live in Denton area and are facing a divorce, contact  our law office at [number type=\"1\"]. Our phones are answered 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, so you can receive quick responses to your most pressing legal concerns. Our attorneys handle dissolution of marriage cases for clients throughout North Texas, including Lewisville, Denton, Flower Mound and other surrounding areas.  Contact us today!</p>\r\n', 'Divorce', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '348-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-26 07:57:44', '2013-10-26 07:57:44', '', '348', 'http://www.brentbowen.com/348-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
