rsue whichever option leads to the better result.\r\n\r\nIn each case we handle, we place a strong emphasis on providing lasting results for the client we represent. Many people who are arrested on criminal charges are facing difficult personal challenges that may involve chemical dependency, mental illness or anger management issues. In cases where clients may benefit from assistance and ask for our help, we are pleased to provide assistance with the location of appropriate medical and mental health professionals.\r\n<h3>Contact a Texas Criminal Defense Attorney</h3>\r\nTo schedule a free consultation to learn more about your rights and options, call our Denton office at [number type=\"1\"] or contact our criminal defense lawyers by e-mail.', 'Criminal Defense', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '290-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-29 10:52:35', '2013-10-29 10:52:35', '', '290', 'http://www.brentbowen.com/290-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
