zation course referred to in the Denton County Standing Orders.\r\n\r\nDenton County Friends of The Family: <a href=\"http://www.dcfof.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.dcfof.org</a>\r\nProvides assistance and classes for victims of Domestic Violence.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://west.thomson.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thomson – West (formerly West Group)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.uscourts.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">U.S. Courts</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.westlaw.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Westlaw</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Business and Finance</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.uschamber.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">United States Chamber of Commerce</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Government</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.firstgov.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">FirstGov</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.loc.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Library of Congress</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.house.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">U.S. House of Representatives</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.senate.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">U.S. Senate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.whitehouse.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">White House</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>General</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.nws.noaa.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">National Weather Service</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://maps.yahoo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yahoo! Maps</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.yellowpages.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">YellowPages.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>News</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">New York Times</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.newspapers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Newspapers Online</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.usatoday.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=